Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:10.30,0:00:16.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在被星光照射的頂屋裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:16.90,0:00:23.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,獨自一人聆聽著天空的聲音
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:23.55,0:00:29.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,用玻璃的繃帶遮住眼睛行走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:30.20,0:00:36.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大家都是孤獨的馬戲團孩子啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:37.85,0:00:44.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,孤身一人的悲傷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:44.10,0:00:45.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,震動的繃帶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:45.87,0:00:50.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,撼動著心靈……
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:57.35,0:01:06.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,用溫柔的眼神期待與某人的相會
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:14.05,0:01:21.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在我耳邊細語「請留在我身邊」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:21.27,0:01:26.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Silent Voice
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:31.56,0:01:35.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,第三十七話 新亞加瑪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:48.32,0:01:53.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,落下殖民地計劃成功後\n哈曼就趕往宇宙鎮壓
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:56.79,0:01:58.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們得到這個消息
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:58.84,0:02:02.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,便離開挪威前往宇宙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:15.12,0:02:18.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,檢查艙內壓力,IMU航路管理\n顯示
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:18.79,0:02:22.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,北28度36分30時32分
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:22.71,0:02:25.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還是告別了亞加瑪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:25.41,0:02:28.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是艘好船阿,真可惜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:28.07,0:02:31.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,船並沒有沉\n只是轉給卡拉巴使用罷了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:31.33,0:02:35.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,並沒有浪費掉\n發動前一分鐘,開始倒數讀秒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:38.28,0:02:39.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大家坐穩了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:39.83,0:02:43.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就算是最新式的\n起飛還是很危險阿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:43.46,0:02:46.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,說這種話的人,不是在最安全的艙內嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:46.63,0:02:50.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別抱怨了,摔下去大家一樣會死\n你別烏鴉嘴了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:50.68,0:02:55.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,總算是平安來到這裏了\n這是因為哈曼的戰力轉移到宇宙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:55.55,0:03:00.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們又不能殺死地球聯邦政府的高官
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:00.05,0:03:04.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們救不了任何人阿\n又一定要坐上這太空船
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:05.38,0:03:07.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,捷度...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:07.61,0:03:09.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一切都還沒結束
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:09.42,0:03:12.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,地球的人們只是\n將第三號殖民地送給哈曼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:12.75,0:03:15.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是懷疑這麼做能解決事情嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:15.68,0:03:17.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以我們才要加油
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:18.74,0:03:20.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好,我要加油
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:20.79,0:03:23.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,艾莉!你在幹什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:24.86,0:03:26.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是我個人的自由阿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:23.32,0:04:26.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不久後就會進入\n第四殖民地的暗礁空域
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:39.65,0:04:42.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,艦長,聽說到了拉比安羅茲阿\n在那邊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:53.98,0:04:59.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是什麼船,跟亞加瑪一模一樣\n那是新戰艦,新亞加瑪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:59.49,0:05:05.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,新亞加瑪?在格拉那達做的船?\n那就是我們的新船了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:05.73,0:05:07.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,新亞加瑪...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:19.01,0:05:20.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,艾美莉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:22.68,0:05:26.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,辛苦你們了\n布拉度艦長,亞加瑪的各位
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:26.81,0:05:29.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,謝謝你,代理艦長
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:29.72,0:05:30.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:30.70,0:05:34.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,歡迎回來,捷度\n你好..
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:36.65,0:05:40.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,難得你們能平安回來\n那個中年人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:43.62,0:05:48.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,布拉度艦長,不好意思\n剛抵達就有事要跟你談   是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:48.38,0:05:52.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,艦長,不是應該先去參觀新亞加瑪?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:52.49,0:05:53.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,說的也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:54.45,0:05:58.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂\n米莉,帶捷度他們去看新亞加瑪吧  是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:58.42,0:05:59.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,艦長
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:59.37,0:06:00.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:01.21,0:06:05.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,新亞加瑪的意思向亞加瑪發誓
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:05.17,0:06:07.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,向亞加瑪發誓?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:07.08,0:06:09.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因為它繼承了\n亞加瑪的設計思想阿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:11.30,0:06:16.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好厲害,全是最新儀器\n這可以賣的很高價錢的阿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:16.25,0:06:19.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,莫迪,你還擺脫不了\n撿破爛的習性嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:22.20,0:06:25.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是,拿這艘船當退休金\n就差不多了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:25.88,0:06:27.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,退休金?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:27.48,0:06:31.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,去第三殖民地打敗哈曼\n戰爭不就結束了嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:31.25,0:06:35.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,到時候我們不就變成沒用了\n用這艘船開貨運公司
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:35.97,0:06:38.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,新亞加瑪運輸公司
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:40.13,0:06:42.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎樣?很好操縱嗎?\n喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:42.65,0:06:45.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,主炮的控制裝置是這個吧..
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:45.66,0:06:48.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,米加利子炮的系統有三重
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:48.70,0:06:52.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,炮座跟艦橋都可以操作\n那太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:55.42,0:07:01.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,全體人全準備戰鬥,炮擊組\n炮火不夠密集,你們在幹什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:01.01,0:07:03.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,笨蛋\n你自己為你是誰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:03.51,0:07:05.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,外行人\n對阿...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:09.98,0:07:11.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這就是米加利子炮嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:14.57,0:07:17.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,發射甲板,開始誘導
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:17.39,0:07:19.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,艾莉,你懂嗎?\n你看著吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:24.31,0:07:26.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們這些人!\n放開我!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:29.41,0:07:31.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們在幹什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:31.41,0:07:34.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們在檢查儀器\n誰准許的?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:34.28,0:07:37.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,檢查自己的船有什麼不對嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:37.08,0:07:38.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,自己的船?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:39.96,0:07:42.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們什麼都不知道嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:42.84,0:07:46.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼意思?\n我們沒有必要對小鬼解釋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:46.75,0:07:49.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你說誰是小鬼!\n算了吧,捷度
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:49.64,0:07:52.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是艾美莉代理艦長\n准許他們進入這裏的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:52.86,0:07:56.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這件事我倒沒有聽說過\n算了,你們滾出去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:56.30,0:07:57.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你說什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:58.34,0:07:59.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可惡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:59.39,0:08:04.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別生氣了\n大家去MS甲板吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:15.44,0:08:18.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那就是奧干的做法嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:18.25,0:08:21.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,新人類只是小孩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:21.02,0:08:24.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,太任性,不會聽從命令
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:24.83,0:08:28.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就因為這理由\n要求捷度他們離開亞加瑪嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:28.49,0:08:31.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們在地球\n與新吉翁作戰的期間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:31.63,0:08:34.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們剛好也獲得了\n重建組織的時間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:34.62,0:08:37.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不再需要依靠小孩子了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:37.18,0:08:39.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是他們救過我們很多次阿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:39.61,0:08:41.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,今後不再需要了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:41.87,0:08:47.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哈曼已經在第三殖民地落地生根\n所以更需要他們的力量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:47.47,0:08:49.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,今後的問題是大人的問題
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:49.51,0:08:52.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,想想重新編隊\n加速訓練駕駛員吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:52.74,0:08:55.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,意思是不需要\n亞加瑪的就船員嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:55.91,0:09:01.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,布拉度艦長你例外,你來指揮新亞加瑪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:01.47,0:09:03.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不接受這種任性的要求
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:03.73,0:09:08.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你沒資格選擇\n做選擇的是奧干的參謀總部
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:11.55,0:09:13.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,聽見了嗎?\n噓
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:13.31,0:09:15.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,偷聽不好啊..\n安靜點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:21.59,0:09:23.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快讓開
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:23.92,0:09:26.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,米查!\n你敢直呼我的名子?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:26.35,0:09:29.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們跟地球聯邦的大官\n根本就是一樣的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:29.74,0:09:34.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,艦長,你容許他們這麼說嗎?\n當然不可能了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:34.01,0:09:40.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對阿,艦長忍耐不去見在地球的太太和小孩\n急著趕回宇宙的阿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:40.79,0:09:44.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是阿,早知道這樣\n我就想辦法去見他們了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:47.90,0:09:49.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不...那是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:49.97,0:09:52.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們這些小孩\n竟敢插嘴軍方的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:52.49,0:09:55.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們有實戰經驗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:55.61,0:09:57.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,亞加瑪的計劃沒有成功
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:57.94,0:10:02.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是因為奧干的參謀\n原本就無意與哈曼打起來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:02.11,0:10:03.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你說奧幹不想打
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:03.92,0:10:07.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不然為何\n把第三殖民地送給哈曼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:07.41,0:10:10.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是...地球聯邦的人...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:10.38,0:10:13.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,總之是奧干沒有及時阻止
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:13.48,0:10:17.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,月球與地球的人\n都不瞭解殖民地的痛苦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:17.49,0:10:18.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們真可惡阿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:18.58,0:10:20.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,指揮官,請冷靜下來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:21.03,0:10:25.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,布拉度艦長,你教導不周\n小孩子才這麼囂張
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:25.61,0:10:28.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒辦法,他們學不懂基本禮儀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:28.52,0:10:30.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也很困擾\n艦長
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:32.15,0:10:33.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,敵襲嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:55.12,0:10:56.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,伊莉亞.帕桌\n是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:58.33,0:10:59.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:05.35,0:11:06.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,馬士文大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:06.84,0:11:11.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我落下殖民地\n奪走太多數人的生命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:11.28,0:11:16.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我已不適合這朵玫瑰了\n馬士文大人,你太浪漫了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:16.04,0:11:18.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,騎士本來就應該有柔情的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:18.83,0:11:21.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只有武勇的話\n豈不跟野獸一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:21.63,0:11:24.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而這樣的人\n在香格里拉太多了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:24.52,0:11:27.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,馬士文大人,偵查部隊回來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:30.02,0:11:34.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,敵人是亞加瑪型的巡洋艦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:34.06,0:11:39.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,亞加瑪型?是新造戰艦嗎?\n調偵查部隊回來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:39.42,0:11:43.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,進入第一戰鬥狀態\n茲沙隊準備發動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:44.09,0:11:48.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對敵人發動威嚇射擊\n10秒1連射
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:48.17,0:11:53.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,全速開進敵人空域\n茲沙隊迂迴避過炮擊火線
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:53.76,0:11:56.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,回轉角度15度,開始炮擊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:14.68,0:12:17.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們沒資格出動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:17.22,0:12:20.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這樣下去拉比安羅茲\n與新亞加瑪會被擊沉的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:20.85,0:12:24.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是軍人,只能遵守命令
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:24.27,0:12:26.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,幸好我不是軍人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:26.00,0:12:28.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們在幹什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:29.21,0:12:33.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這樣下去新亞加瑪\n和拉比安羅茲會被擊沉的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:33.05,0:12:36.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,胡說八道\n你太囂張了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:36.05,0:12:38.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,懂得駕駛MS算什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:38.77,0:12:41.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,住手\n他是小孩子阿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:41.05,0:12:44.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們在幹什麼?\n他們在鬧事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:44.27,0:12:46.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這時候自己人還起什麼內哄?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:46.39,0:12:48.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是這些小孩子違反命令
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:48.90,0:12:50.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在不是提那種事的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:53.70,0:12:59.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,被直接命中了\n你們去吧,別輸給小孩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:01.57,0:13:03.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,已經明顯輸了阿...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:16.27,0:13:17.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:17.28,0:13:20.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,能源填充完畢,快啟動炮台\n鎖定完畢,炮台開始迎擊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:21.62,0:13:24.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們真能幹阿\n可是,艦長
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:24.45,0:13:27.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們去塔台操做!\n為什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:27.07,0:13:30.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,接到命令還要問理由嗎?\n知道!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:30.46,0:13:32.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,了不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:32.00,0:13:34.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,把合體的武器解除開來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:34.13,0:13:36.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,艦長\n你們倆到裏面吧  是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:37.35,0:13:39.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,新亞加瑪快出動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:39.47,0:13:43.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快把孩子們叫下來\n不可能,沒那時間了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:43.48,0:13:47.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,放新亞加瑪出去\n不然會同歸於盡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:47.35,0:13:48.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,代理艦長!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:51.06,0:13:53.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,準備發動\n武器全體解除
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:53.67,0:13:54.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好!新亞加瑪...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:54.95,0:13:56.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,布拉度艦長\n咦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:56.41,0:14:00.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,下一句話由我說吧\n新亞加瑪,出動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:07.27,0:14:11.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,飛彈全部發射完畢\n好,後退,其他的交給後續部隊吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:14.89,0:14:19.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,敵人後退\n好,下一波會再來,小心點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:20.50,0:14:23.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,比查,接下來交給你指揮\n咦?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:23.71,0:14:26.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,想當司令官就得學會適應
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:26.23,0:14:30.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我去艦內巡查\n好,我要指揮了阿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:30.35,0:14:32.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,玩是可以...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:32.24,0:14:33.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你別當真阿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:33.75,0:14:37.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,知道大家的意思吧?\n這可不是在玩阿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:38.58,0:14:40.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還是不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:40.08,0:14:41.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我叫你讓開\n不行   小孩子讓開
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:41.11,0:14:43.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們在幹什麼?洗達,冠武
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:43.35,0:14:44.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,布拉度叔叔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:44.30,0:14:47.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這些人不聽命令,離開炮台
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:47.53,0:14:50.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們是艦橋人員\n你不該
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:50.14,0:14:53.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,派我們去炮台的\n因為我們是新人嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:53.40,0:14:57.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在以有實戰經驗的人優先\n可是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:57.62,0:15:02.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,B舷發現一架MS\n為什麼只是一架?艦長
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:02.40,0:15:04.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他不是全權委託你嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:04.60,0:15:07.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是...\n我去迎戰   好,去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:09.68,0:15:12.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,新造的戰艦嗎?\n是好的誘餌
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:20.77,0:15:22.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,洗達,冠武
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:28.29,0:15:30.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,洗達,冠武
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:37.23,0:15:40.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,捷度.桑達,ZZ高達,出動\n請
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:46.47,0:15:47.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒見過的MS
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:51.16,0:15:53.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是高達?真不敢相信
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:56.50,0:15:57.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好快,在哪裏?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:03.47,0:16:06.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你在看哪裏啊?\n什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:10.64,0:16:11.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:12.50,0:16:14.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,剛才那是怎嚜回事?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:14.75,0:16:20.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,完全沒有彈幕,炮台\n炮台沒人  什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:20.18,0:16:21.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,艦長到外面了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:22.47,0:16:24.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,轉由艦橋控制炮擊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:25.43,0:16:29.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,艦長在那小艇上面\n太亂來了,會被擊毀的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:29.64,0:16:34.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我駕駛MK2去支援吧\n艾莉,別擅自出去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:37.00,0:16:38.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是新亞加瑪的小艇?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:40.67,0:16:42.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你在發什麼呆?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:43.57,0:16:44.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,又來了...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:46.52,0:16:50.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是什麼裝置?ZZ高達\n好像電流傳到全身似的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:55.77,0:16:57.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,茲沙隊全部回艦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:57.79,0:17:02.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼?為什麼回來?\n戰鬥還沒結束阿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:02.14,0:17:03.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,彈藥用完了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:03.93,0:17:07.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼?叫他們去甲板\n我去教訓他們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:12.14,0:17:14.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等等阿,現在就救你們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:17.41,0:17:20.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是繩子,快抓住
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:26.52,0:17:29.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是在幹什麼阿?\n救人優先
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:29.25,0:17:32.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,布拉度艦長?\n他們算是我的部下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:32.02,0:17:33.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,需要我用ZZ高達嗎...\n不必
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:33.91,0:17:38.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我帶他們去拉比安羅茲\n你監視敵人    是..是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:41.27,0:17:44.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可惡,不准發射飛到這裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:50.02,0:17:51.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好快
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:52.12,0:17:53.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不會輸給任何人的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:58.92,0:18:00.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好強的力量阿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:03.91,0:18:04.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,想逃嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:07.25,0:18:10.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,被敵人牽著鼻子走\n只會消耗過多能量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:10.92,0:18:13.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,該怎麼辦...\n對了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:21.55,0:18:24.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼還不出來?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:24.00,0:18:26.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為什麼那駕駛員\n能抵擋住我?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:42.14,0:18:44.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,ZZ高達在哪裏?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:45.15,0:18:46.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,找到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:48.15,0:18:51.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼?\n是看不起我嗎?還是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:54.29,0:18:57.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,原來你是有勇無謀的呆子\n高達
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:00.10,0:19:01.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你在瞄準哪裏?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:04.14,0:19:06.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你完了\n什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:11.71,0:19:14.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是什麼回事?\n就是這樣!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:24.40,0:19:27.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是什麼作戰方法\n太看不起人了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:27.17,0:19:28.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是認真的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:29.15,0:19:30.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只穿太空衣,你想幹什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:30.98,0:19:33.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,做事不能只照課本做的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:33.23,0:19:35.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我要殺死你阿\n你試試吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:39.84,0:19:42.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你太笨了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:44.19,0:19:45.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,又...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:47.83,0:19:49.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我絕對不會原諒你的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:53.87,0:19:55.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果事先沒損傷的話...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:01.94,0:20:05.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,捷度,布拉度艦長怎麼了?\n去拉比安羅茲了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:09.07,0:20:11.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,到底發生什麼事了?捷度
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:16.95,0:20:19.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們的激光劍\n是拿來幹什麼的?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:19.54,0:20:22.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,難道你們完全沒有\n與高達對抗的志氣嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:22.71,0:20:28.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是,馬士文大人\n不准頂嘴,你沒資格說話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:28.22,0:20:29.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,伊莉亞,你回來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:35.46,0:20:36.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,玫瑰花...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:40.79,0:20:45.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對不起\n我被ZZ高達的駕駛員打敗了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:46.96,0:20:49.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,玫瑰,哈曼大人的玫瑰...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:50.32,0:20:55.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,ZZ高達,捷度.桑達..\n那個駕駛員..
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:55.45,0:20:59.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,原來...他就是捷度.桑達
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:06.08,0:21:07.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,捷度,辛苦你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:07.94,0:21:10.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,敵人的船怎麼樣了?\n還在阿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:10.36,0:21:14.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快離開拉比安羅茲吧\n敵人的目標是我們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:14.14,0:21:16.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,待在一起的話\n連拉比安羅茲也會捲入戰爭的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:16.56,0:21:18.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,布拉度艦長,怎麼辦?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:18.79,0:21:23.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請他在拉比安羅茲休養一陣子\n他老了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:23.06,0:21:25.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們經常給他惹麻煩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:25.49,0:21:27.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,布拉度艦長才不停長出白頭髮的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:27.68,0:21:31.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,總之我們先往月球方向移動\n對吧,比查?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:31.38,0:21:36.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒錯,最終的目標是潛入\n第三號殖民地跟哈曼單挑決鬥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:36.89,0:21:38.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,去吧,代理艦長
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:38.60,0:21:41.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好,全體人員各就各位\n是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:41.61,0:21:44.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,新亞加瑪,出動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:53.05,0:21:54.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,又要分別了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:54.43,0:21:57.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,發出通訊,祝亞加瑪馬到成功
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:57.89,0:22:02.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快要說再見了,布拉度艦長\n那可不行阿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:06.48,0:22:08.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,布拉度艦長
